<body>
 <p><strong>Add / Edit Organization</strong></p>
<p>This screen will allow you to add a new Organization or edit an existing Organization</p>

<p>Enter / Edit the details: Organization Name, Contact Person, Email Address, Phone Number, Organization Address</p>

<p>Upload the Organization Logo by clicking on the 'Select file' button and selecting the Image file. You can view the uploaded logo by clicking on the 'View Logo' button. </p>

<p>Select the Status of the Organization (Active / Deactive) and click on the Save Button to save the Organization details</p>

<p>To delete the Organization select the Organization and click on the Delete button</p>

<p><font color='red'>Important: Deleting the Organization will delete all reference Sites and Sensors for the deleted Organization</font></p>
</body>
